136
00:07:47,959 --> 00:07:49,939
You should take note of that.

137
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,900
Okay.

138
00:08:03,079 --> 00:08:05,220
Are you afraid of the dark?

139
00:08:18,199 --> 00:08:20,579
(Why am I feeling sorry for her?)

140
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:24,819
There are candles

141
00:08:24,839 --> 00:08:26,300
in the cabinet.

142
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,699
Okay.

143
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,340
I'll go get some.

144
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,939
It's the second drawer.

145
00:08:53,759 --> 00:08:55,758
(She still has Xu Yiqing's stuff
with her.)

146
00:08:55,759 --> 00:08:59,320
(Xu Yiqing, Deputy General Manager)

147
